{"code": 0, "data": {"allow_search": false, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 213069, "create_time": 1655119759, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "发展是硬道理，如果连中等发达国家都达不到，建立再完善的民主法治都没有用", "timestamp": 1655119759}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 213073, "create_time": 1655119844, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "也许确实是有这种人，但是地方雇佣黑社会打杀上访、信访人员显然是更成熟的产业链（对每个地方都有考核指标，某个地方上访太多会不合格），一般人不是走投无路也不会这样上访。", "timestamp": 1655119844}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 213078, "create_time": 1655119909, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "Re Alice: 世界上达到中等发达国家的才有多少，其他国家的人也得过日子。我觉得现在最大的一个问题，就是很多人总以为自己活在发达国家，而短期内这本来就是不现实的。", "timestamp": 1655119909}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 213081, "create_time": 1655119955, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Bob: 确实如此，但是也很两难。一方面是人民保护自己的权力得不到支持，另一方面又是对法律资源的恶意挤占", "timestamp": 1655119955}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 213085, "create_time": 1655120024, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Bob: 联想到《我不是潘金莲》那部电影，感觉还有一种情况也是人民确实缺乏正确的法律意识，但是根本就没有人愿意给她解释清楚", "timestamp": 1655120024}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": true, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 213089, "create_time": 1655120038, "is_blocked": true, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "", "timestamp": 1655120038}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 213093, "create_time": 1655120049, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "专门闹事的该罚罚，赔偿维稳成本", "timestamp": 1655120049}, {"author_title": "", "bloc